 \text{Distance} = \sqrt{9,000,000 + 16,000,000} 
 \text{Distance} = \sqrt{25,000,000} 
 \text{Distance} \approx 5,000 \text{ feet} 

Therefore, Oliver must climb 5,000 feet to reach Stanley's comb.

The answer is: 5,000 feet

